221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"茶記"},{"pid":"2e4697c07c9af8aead79432a54982ef560dbf82c","tid":140280,"uid":49976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"食糖水/ 甜品,e.g.許留山"},{"pid":"e8e443d0dc60563c3b5f253e9016dba1ccd89815","tid":140280,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇架妹介紹返俾大家識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想地道D，頭先有人提左中環果邊，食完仲可以過老蘭</blockquote><br />\n去過幾次日本都識唔到架妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個架仔係我上年去日本玩couchsurfing識，係佢屋企訓過幾晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c4ced2587ce8ff8ae10b6c54f70a133261fb0c","tid":140280,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"周圍去嘅 不如去睇啲有特色嘅野<br />\n渡海小輪 舊區 電車 愛丁堡廣場 香港大會堂<br />\n終審法院 油麻地/深水埗差館 南/北九龍裁判司署 粉嶺地院<br />\n好多數唔曬"},{"pid":"7bb64449de52462a70bf49e26f89817840172211","tid":140280,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周圍去嘅 不如去睇啲有特色嘅野<br />\n渡海小輪 舊區 電車 愛丁堡廣場 香港大會堂<br />\n終審法院 油麻地/深水埗差館 南/北九龍裁判司署 粉嶺地院<br />\n好多數唔曬</blockquote><br />\n同意特別係搭船同電車<br />\n重有帶佢入長洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3ebf61e8b3df5df2ba5e5788cae62057eb62b5","tid":140280,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周圍去嘅 不如去睇啲有特色嘅野<br />\n渡海小輪 舊區 電車 愛丁堡廣場 香港大會堂<br />\n終審法院 油麻地/深水埗差館 南/北九龍裁判司署 粉嶺地院<br />\n好多數唔曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深水埗正丫<br />\n倀個潮式粉面就行差館<br />\n之後去鴨記睇下，再食個公和豆花配3寶<br />\n最後帶佢去睇港式妖怪通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就半日行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58540fa5e0233622a7675e1de2127539dd95ef60","tid":140280,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>周圍去嘅 不如去睇啲有特色嘅野<br />\n渡海小輪 舊區 電車 愛丁堡廣場 香港大會堂<br />\n終審法院 油麻地/深水埗差館 南/北九龍裁判司署 粉嶺地院<br />\n好多數唔曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深水埗正丫<br />\n倀個潮式粉面就行差館<br />\n之後去鴨記睇下，再食個公和豆花配3寶<br />\n最後帶佢去睇港式妖怪通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就半日行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16762532aeac760aca68c67661909caed80e321","tid":140280,"uid":60187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"Show me your love 飯"},{"pid":"bb7ce4941168da3cd4786b15b1fa936d9436c38a","tid":140280,"uid":15818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"無理由唔去香港個富士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4c242c11be6460f92d04176c7d48fc4e3b1341","tid":140280,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"梗係帶佢食燒味飯啦，只前睇個Post個巴打帶個日本客食叉燒飯感動到留眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514e7c341e8c6c77ea80adb46e9a69de1d74e76c","tid":140280,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無理由唔去香港個富士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港名菜：北菇雞"},{"pid":"5938a96be5099ad5700dc5cf0fb1eb04af3d1623","tid":140280,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"